      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver verified against at least one canonical rotating-flow benchmark with documented order-of-accuracy confirmation.",
      "rationale": "Taylor-Couette flow and lid-driven cavity benchmarks confirm second-order spatial accuracy. Rotating reference frame implementation verified against analytical solution for solid-body rotation. No code defects identified relevant to the CPB hemolysis QoI."
    },
