      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) < 5% for hemolysis scalar and velocity magnitude at representative operating point.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study (2.1M, 5.8M, 14.2M cells) performed at 4.5 L/min / 2500 RPM. Richardson extrapolation yields GCI of 2.3% for NIH and 1.9% for area-averaged outlet velocity. Medium mesh (5.8M) selected for production runs. Prism layer y+ maintained between 1 and 5 throughout the flow domain."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
