      "rationale": "FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry used in both validation experiments and COU simulations. Bovine blood surrogate (glycerin-water, matched viscosity) used in bench hemolysis tests. Operating points span 2.5–5.5 L/min covering the COU range. Geometric similarity confirmed; no untested extrapolation beyond validated envelope claimed in the COU decision."
    },
