    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to gradation 1 per MRL 2 requirements table and confirmed not-assessed. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. RH < 1 acceptance criterion met at all evaluated operating points. Assessment team recommends acceptance for regulatory submission.",
